overview: Every big story has a beginning. Every big contest has a preliminary part. Every beauty queen has a past. And behind it all, there is a Man who made it possible: You. You are the owner, the judge and the god of the illustrious beauty contest called Miss Spectacular, an event where gorgeous girls from all around the world compete for the title of the Beauty Queen. But as it happens with competitions like this, there are jealousy, rivalry, intrigue and seduction behind the stage... these girls will do whatever it takes to be the winner.
title: Beauty Contest
